title
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an abbreviation of <i>certificate of title</i>, a copy of the entry in the land titles register recording the identity and ownership of a piece of land and any legal encumbrances on it.
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
